cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL

The paper proposes a neural network approach to capture functional connectivities among anatomic brain regions, which involves machine learning and neuroscience. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) since the paper deals with neural networks and image data. Additionally, the paper uses Support Vector Machines (SVM) as a classifier, which falls under the sub-category cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper also involves natural language processing (NLP) techniques to analyze the text data, which falls under the sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language).
